"SECTION 5. IC 25-26-13-4, AS AMENDED BY P.L.93-2024,
SECTION 186, IS AMENDED TO READ AS FOLLOWS
[EFFECTIVE JULY 1, 2026]: Sec. 4. (a) The board may:
(1) adopt rules under IC 4-22-2 for implementing and enforcing
this chapter;
(2) establish requirements and tests to determine the moral,
physical, intellectual, educational, scientific, technical, and
professional qualifications for applicants for pharmacists'
